headline: Staying In Franklin Resources For The Dividend
summary: Franklin Resources has record sales, but profitability is down. Learn why BEN stock remains a dividend play, with a 7% CAGR expected for future growth.

headline: Wamco Clients, Staff Head for Exits as Ken Leech Heads to Court
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Outwardly, all is upbeat at Western Asset Management, which has invited its staff and clients to celebrate the New Year by watching the Rose Parade from Wamco’s balconies in Pasadena, California, and cheer on the firm’s flower-bedecked entry, “Float Like a Butterfly.” The parade’s theme is “Best Day Ever!”Most Read from BloombergHong Kong's Expat Party Hub Reshaped by Chinese InfluxHow California Sees the World, and ItselfCity Hall Is HiringLondon’s Tube Fares Are Set to Rise by 4
